OL,5, Leading lawyers say they will refuse to
OL,6, prosecute climate protesters or        
OL,7, represent new fossil fuel projects.    
OL,9,FMore than 120 lawyers have vowed to not
OL,10,Fact against activists from groups such 
OL,11,Fas Extinction Rebellion and Just Stop  
OL,12,FOil who are "exercising their          
OL,13,Fdemocratic right of peaceful protest". 
OL,15,FThey have published a "Declaration of  
OL,16,FConscience", and face the prospect of  
OL,17,Fdisciplinary action.                   
OL,19,FThe chair of the Bar Council Nick      
OL,20,FVineall KC said it was "disappointing".
